
# Compilation

```
    make
```

# Usage

```
    ./lsscp
```

Shows parameters and options of the program


# Jupyter/Ipython

The IPython Notebook used to analyze the data is at the root of the archive ("heuristics.ipynb").

* Install Jupyter/IPython, Python 3, python-matplotlib, numpy and scipy

* Run Jupyter with

```
    jupyter notebook
```

* Go to "http://localhost:8888" and open the file

* In the menu "Cell" there is a button "Run All" that will launch every cell. It may take a while to finish.

* The instances files must be in a directory "instances" below the notebook. The results are stored in a directory "results" below the notebook.